# ── Secrets — NEVER publish ───────────────────────────────────────────────
# The update-signing private key lives in ~/.tauri, outside this tree. These
# patterns are a backstop in case a key is ever copied in here by accident.
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
*.pfx
*password*.txt
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Internal planning documents — NEVER publish ───────────────────────────
# The repo is public (source-available). Product strategy, the PLAID planning
# artifacts and the proprietary style research stay in the working tree only.
# Public docs added by later tasks (docs/legal/, docs/runbooks/, docs/daw-matrix.md)
# are deliberately NOT covered by these paths and remain tracked.
/vision.json
/scripts/validate-vision.js
/docs/gtm.md
/docs/prd.md
/docs/product-roadmap.md
/docs/product-vision.md
/docs/style-research.md

